data.description: Are you looking for a home in Strafford?  How about one within walking distance from the school? If so, this is it!!Great 3 bedroom 2 Bath with an open living room and dining area. Hardwood floors and tile throughout. Home has a bonus Pellet Stove to save money on utilities during the winter. Garage is completely insulated as well. Roof and siding replaced in 2020. New vapor barrier and sump pump installed in October 2023.  In the backyard is two buildings for storage and a kennel. Come see your future home today!
